      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Retrieval comparisons are not meaningful here — all methods\nhave identical retrieval. The real competition is in Selection\nand Generation quality (ROUGE-L, KSR, Faithfulness, Correctness).",
