      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Retrieval metrics (Recall@5, nDCG@5, Evidence Hit Rate) are effectively equal across all three methods (0.986–0.989) because\nthe retriever is fixed — all methods retrieve the same top-20 chunks from Pinecone. These metrics validate the retrieval stage\nbut cannot distinguish the methods. Selection and generation metrics (ROUGE-L, KSR, Faithfulness, Correctness) are where LitePack wins.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
